<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 06:15:54 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>洞察：失去救援希望，一些欧洲太阳能公司前往美国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/losing-hope-rescue-some-european-solar-firms-head-us-2024-04-15/</link><description>欧洲各国政府将于本周采取行动支持其太阳能制造商，但现在已经来不及阻止太阳能电池板制造商梅耶博格(Meyer Burger)打包一家德国工厂将生产转移到美国了。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 06:05:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/losing-hope-rescue-some-european-solar-firms-head-us-2024-04-15/</guid></item><item><title>独家：俄罗斯和中国以废品贸易新铜以规避税收和制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russia-china-trade-new-copper-disguised-scrap-skirt-taxes-sanctions-2024-04-15/</link><description>三名知情人士告诉路透社，俄罗斯铜业公司（RCC）和中国企业通过贸易伪装成废料的新铜盘条来避税并避开西方制裁的影响。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 05:10:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russia-china-trade-new-copper-disguised-scrap-skirt-taxes-sanctions-2024-04-15/</guid></item><item><title>解释者：所罗门群岛举行全国大选之际，中国、卫生系统成为首要问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-health-system-top-issues-solomon-islands-holds-national-election-2024-04-15/</link><description>所罗门群岛将于 4 月 17 日举行全国选举，这是自总理玛纳西·索加瓦雷与中国签署安全协议以来的首次选举，该协议引发了美国和南太平洋邻国的担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 04:04:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-health-system-top-issues-solomon-islands-holds-national-election-2024-04-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示香港必须“牢牢守住”国家安全线维护发展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-hong-kong-must-tightly-hold-national-security-line-safeguard-2024-04-15/</link><description>中国负责香港事务的高级官员在新国安法颁布几周后的一次讲话中表示，香港应“牢牢守住”国家安全底线，以维护发展。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 04:00:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-hong-kong-must-tightly-hold-national-security-line-safeguard-2024-04-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国奇瑞表示将与欧洲优质汽车品牌签署平台合作协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-chery-says-it-will-sign-deal-with-premium-european-auto-brand-over-2024-04-15/</link><description>芜湖汽车制造商奇瑞 (CHERY.UL) 董事长尹同跃周日表示，该公司将与一家欧洲优质品牌签署平台合作协议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 03:47:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-chery-says-it-will-sign-deal-with-premium-european-auto-brand-over-2024-04-15/</guid></item><item><title>IDC 称，由于 iPhone 出货量下降，苹果将第一大手机制造商的位置拱手让给了三星</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-loses-top-phonemaker-spot-samsung-iphone-shipments-drop-idc-says-2024-04-15/</link><description>研究公司 IDC 周日的数据显示，由于争夺第一名的 Android 智能手机制造商的竞争加剧，苹果智能手机出货量在 2024 年第一季度下降了约 10%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 01:54:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-loses-top-phonemaker-spot-samsung-iphone-shipments-drop-idc-says-2024-04-15/</guid></item><item><title>万科称已制定应对短期流动性压力的计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-vanke-says-it-faces-short-term-liquidity-pressure-2024-04-15/</link><description>国有房地产开发商万科表示，该公司面临短期流动性压力和经营困难，但补充称，该公司已准备好“一篮子计划”来稳定业务并削减债务。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 01:37:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-vanke-says-it-faces-short-term-liquidity-pressure-2024-04-15/</guid></item><item><title>中国银行维持政策利率不变，从银行体系中抽走现金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-keeps-policy-rate-unchanged-drains-cash-banking-system-2024-04-15/</link><description>中国央行周一在到期中期贷款展期时，按照普遍预期维持关键政策利率不变，并通过债券工具从银行体系中抽走部分现金。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 01:34:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-keeps-policy-rate-unchanged-drains-cash-banking-system-2024-04-15/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚警方称悉尼持刀袭击者可能以女性为目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-police-say-sydney-knife-attacker-may-have-targeted-women-2024-04-15/</link><description>澳大利亚警方周一表示，在悉尼海滩郊区邦迪一个繁忙的购物中心刺死六人的袭击者可能以女性为目标，全国哀悼遇难者，数百人在现场附近献花。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 00:27:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-police-say-sydney-knife-attacker-may-have-targeted-women-2024-04-15/</guid></item><item><title>美元坚挺，日元下滑，因美国降息预期减弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-stands-tall-us-rate-cut-bets-recede-2024-04-15/</link><description>美元周一企稳，守住2022年以来最大单周涨幅，因中东冲突升级以及美国利率居高不下的前景提供支撑。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 00:25:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-stands-tall-us-rate-cut-bets-recede-2024-04-15/</guid></item><item><title>创纪录的债务成本意味着气候支出可能会将各国推向破产边缘</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/record-debt-costs-mean-climate-spending-could-push-nations-brink-insolvency-2024-04-15/</link><description>波士顿大学牵头发布的一份报告显示，今年新兴国家将支付创纪录的 4000 亿美元来偿还外债，近 40 个国家在未来五年内无法在不冒违约风险的情况下花费气候适应和可持续发展所需的资金。国际货币基金组织/世界银行春季会议前夕。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 00:03:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/record-debt-costs-mean-climate-spending-could-push-nations-brink-insolvency-2024-04-15/</guid></item><item><title>中东冲突席卷市场，亚洲股市下滑，黄金坚挺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-14/</link><description>周一亚洲股市下跌，金价上涨，因伊朗对以色列的报复性袭击引发了对更广泛地区冲突的担忧，令交易员紧张不安，风险情绪受到打击。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 23:58:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-14/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：随着中东紧张局势升级，去风险、寻求安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-14/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 21:47:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-14/</guid></item><item><title>西班牙制药商 Grifols 董事长告诉报纸，将聘请独立董事</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/spanish-drug-maker-grifols-will-bring-independent-directors-chairman-tells-2024-04-14/</link><description>西班牙制药商 Grifols 董事长在周日发表的报纸采访中表示，该公司正与今年股价暴跌作斗争，计划在其审计和薪酬委员会中增加独立董事，以改善其治理。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 11:16:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/spanish-drug-maker-grifols-will-bring-independent-directors-chairman-tells-2024-04-14/</guid></item><item><title>佩雷拉击败希尔卫冕UFC轻重量级冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/pereira-knocks-out-hill-retain-ufc-light-heavyweight-title-2024-04-14/</link><description>周六晚，巴西选手亚历克斯·佩雷拉在首轮淘汰赛中击败贾马哈·希尔，卫冕 UFC 轻重量级冠军，而张伟丽则在周六晚的 UFC 300 比赛中击败严晓楠，卫冕平量级腰带。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 06:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/pereira-knocks-out-hill-retain-ufc-light-heavyweight-title-2024-04-14/</guid></item></channel></rss>